stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Home : initialBehavior (Pinky/Inky/Clyde, exit delay)
    [*] --> Scatter : initialBehavior (Blinky, delay 0)

    Home --> Scatter : ExitTransition done (inside -> outside)

    Scatter --> Chase : scatter duration ends (OnDisable -> chase.Enable)
    Chase --> Scatter : chase duration ends (OnDisable -> scatter.Enable)

    Scatter --> Frightened : PowerPelletEaten (frightened.Enable(duration))
    Chase --> Frightened : PowerPelletEaten

    Frightened --> Scatter : duration ends (Disable)
    Frightened --> Eaten : OnCollision with Pac-Man

    Eaten --> Home : SetPosition(home.inside) + home.Enable(duration)

    note right of Home
        Each "state" is a GhostBehavior MonoBehaviour toggled via
        Enable()/Disable(). GhostBehavior.Enable schedules Disable
        after `duration`; each OnDisable enables the next behavior.
        Frightened forces speedMultiplier = 0.5.
    end note

    note left of Chase
        Chase is one assigned variant:
        GhostChase (Blinky), GhostChaseAmbusher (Pinky),
        GhostChaseBoo (Inky), GhostChaseFlanker (Clyde).
        Ghost.chase is auto-detected in Awake.
    end note
